metadata.name: We Are Gremlin #3054
metadata.description: we Are Gremlin, We are Imaginary Mischievous Sprite, We Are Mischivievous Folkloric, We Are Malfunctions, We Are Unexplained Problem, We Are Fault, We are Difficult to Locate, We Appear in your Dreams, We Are in your Life who are upto no Good, We Are Mischief can range from Trickster-Like Pranks to outright Sabotage, If there are one or More Gremlins in your dreams, it can also mean it's time to prepare for anthing and anything to happen.
